the number of big cats has been decreasing in south asia for 100 years , but conservationists now hope that we can save them .
the number of wild royal bengal tigers in nepal has increased to 198 a 63.6 % increase in five years the survey showed .
tiger body parts are used in traditional chinese medicine .
