you need a 15-minute distance , and typical drones have about that distance .
the reaper drone , for example , has one failure in 10,000 hours , singh said .
part of the reason for this is simply that air travel is dangerous so standards are much higher .
part of the solution , singh said , is planning for every situation : if things fail , the drone has to do something sensible .
